                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Pringle</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-03-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 12,
                                1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Requests Department to suggest that he go on the <hi rend="italic">Ranger</hi> to Araapala to meet Consul Peterson.</p>
            </div>
